[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":610},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191209\u002F1271823341\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191209\u002F1271823341\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191209\u002F1271823341\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191209\u002F1271823341\u002F":585,"related:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191209\u002F1271823341\u002F":594},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2019\u002F12\u002F09\u002Fjavascript-sync-or-async\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":22,"date":568,"description":569,"extension":570,"lang":571,"meta":572,"navigation":573,"path":574,"readingMinutes":575,"seo":576,"standalone":577,"stem":578,"tags":579,"tldr":582,"updated":582,"url":583,"__hash__":584},"content\u002FJavaScript\u002F世界上誤解最大的語言-JavaScript-之-JS-到底是同步與非同步語言.md","世界上誤解最大的語言 JavaScript 之 JS 到底是同步與非同步語言?!","1271823341",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":562},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,34,37,40,116,119,129,139,149,153,161,170,183,186,194,199,202,208,211,216,219,222,509,514,517,537,540,558],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"許多網路文章都可以看到許多人都說 JavaScript 是一個非同步語言，但是經過一些事情觀念驗證後才發現，這個誤解可大了，所以這一篇就來講一下 JavaScript 到底是非同步語言還是同步語言。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"javascript","JavaScript",[16,24,25],{},"JavaScript 在一開始主要是用於瀏覽器上運行的程式語言，也因為 JavaScript 不需要消耗伺服器的資源而非常受歡迎，但早期 JavaScript 只能用於瀏覽器使用，直到後來出現 Node.js，才改變了 JavaScript 這個語言。",[16,27,28,29,33],{},"首先我們在網路上 Google 都會發現人家說 JavaScript 是一個",[30,31,32],"strong",{},"非同步單執行緒語言","。",[16,35,36],{},"首先先講單執行緒，單執行緒的簡單講就是一次只能執行一個動作，這個算好理解。",[16,38,39],{},"那非同步呢?首先同步的意思簡單來講就是「按部就班」的概念，它是一行一行的執行，而非同步則是它不是一行一行執行有可能會跳行執行，所以試著思考一下以下這個範例。",[41,42,47],"pre",{"className":43,"code":44,"language":45,"meta":46,"style":46},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","setTimeout(() => {\n  console.log('a');\n},0);\nconsole.log('b');\n","js","",[48,49,50,70,89,101],"code",{"__ignoreMap":46},[51,52,55,59,63,67],"span",{"class":53,"line":54},"line",1,[51,56,58],{"class":57},"sj_SG","setTimeout",[51,60,62],{"class":61},"sMAXC","(() ",[51,64,66],{"class":65},"sWyjQ","=>",[51,68,69],{"class":61}," {\n",[51,71,73,76,79,82,86],{"class":53,"line":72},2,[51,74,75],{"class":61},"  console.",[51,77,78],{"class":57},"log",[51,80,81],{"class":61},"(",[51,83,85],{"class":84},"sTRMh","'a'",[51,87,88],{"class":61},");\n",[51,90,92,95,99],{"class":53,"line":91},3,[51,93,94],{"class":61},"},",[51,96,98],{"class":97},"sCcAr","0",[51,100,88],{"class":61},[51,102,104,107,109,111,114],{"class":53,"line":103},4,[51,105,106],{"class":61},"console.",[51,108,78],{"class":57},[51,110,81],{"class":61},[51,112,113],{"class":84},"'b'",[51,115,88],{"class":61},[16,117,118],{},"上面這個經典範例中，許多文章都是用這個範例來介紹 JavaScript 是一個非同步語言，因為優先出現的是 b 而非 a，但是事實上真的代表 JavaScript 是非同步語言嗎?並不是，Why?",[16,120,121,122,125,126,128],{},"JavaScript 在執行的時候並沒有忽略 ",[48,123,124],{},"setTimeout()"," 這一行語法，而是將 ",[48,127,58],{}," 放置在 JavaScript 的一個特性中，也就是所謂的事件佇列 (event quete)。",[16,130,131,132,33],{},"而事件佇列在卡斯柏老師文章中有非常詳細的 ",[133,134,138],"a",{"href":135,"rel":136},"https:\u002F\u002Fwcc723.github.io\u002Fjavascript\u002F2017\u002F12\u002F07\u002Fjavascript-event-queue\u002F",[137],"nofollow","範例說明",[16,140,141,142,145,146,148],{},"JavaScript 在執行的時候是依照同步的概念去執行的，當遇到需要",[30,143,144],{},"非同步的事件","，例如：",[48,147,58],{}," 此時 JavaScript 就會將它丟進事件佇列中，並執行下一行。",[12,150,152],{"id":151},"javascript-是一個同步語言","JavaScript 是一個同步語言",[16,154,155,156,160],{},"其實我們也可以從一些文章抽絲剝解翻到 JavaScript 是一個同步語言，例如我先前寫的 ",[133,157,159],{"href":158},"\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190515\u002F1176852332\u002F","[JS奇怪的世界]No.6 執行環境:程式執行 "," 就有提到「創造完變數後才會開始執行一行一行執行並賦與值」。",[16,162,163,164,169],{},"此外還有 stackoverflow 中的其中一篇文章 ",[133,165,168],{"href":166,"rel":167},"https:\u002F\u002Fstackoverflow.com\u002Fquestions\u002F2035645\u002Fwhen-is-javascript-synchronous",[137],"When is JavaScript synchronous?"," 底下也有許多人提到",[171,172,173,177,180],"ul",{},[174,175,176],"li",{},"JavaScript is always synchronous and single-threaded. (JavaScript 一直都是同步語言且是單執行緒。)",[174,178,179],{},"JavaScript is single threaded and has a synchronous execution model (JavaScript 是一個單執行緒並且具有同步執行特性的語言)",[174,181,182],{},"JavaScript is single-threaded, and all the time you work on a normal synchronous code-flow execution. (JavaScript 是一個單執行緒並且會依照程式碼同步執行)",[16,184,185],{},"那為什麼那麼多人會誤以為 JavaScript 是一個非同步語言呢?主要原因就是 JavaScript 的事件佇列這個特性導致。",[16,187,188,189],{},"最後 Medium 上也有一篇文章提到 JavaScript 是一個同步語言 → ",[133,190,193],{"href":191,"rel":192},"https:\u002F\u002Fmedium.com\u002Fbetter-programming\u002Fis-javascript-synchronous-or-asynchronous-what-the-hell-is-a-promise-7aa9dd8f3bfb",[137],"Is JavaScript Synchronous or Asynchronous? What the Hell is a Promise?",[171,195,196],{},[174,197,198],{},"JavaScript is Synchronous (JavaScript 是同步語言)",[16,200,201],{},"在這一篇 Medium 底下有這幾張圖我覺得相當不錯，在一開始 JavaScript 是先執行過一次程式碼",[16,203,204],{},[205,206],"img",{"alt":22,"src":207},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F1%20DeTnKC6L2eMHj9ICv4k4Eg.jpeg",[16,209,210],{},"後來再將需要做非同步的事件丟進事件佇列中",[16,212,213],{},[205,214],{"alt":22,"src":215},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F1%209iOmFwC3PWUD8RFLsxzBXQ.jpeg",[16,217,218],{},"我們可以看到 JavaScript 一開始是會將所有程式碼執行一遍，並將需要做非同步事件的程式碼(function)丟進事件佇列中。",[16,220,221],{},"所以我們也可以試著還原看看圖片中的程式碼",[41,223,225],{"className":43,"code":224,"language":45,"meta":46,"style":46},"function A() {\n  console.log('A');\n}\nfunction B() {\n  console.log('B');\n}\nfunction C() {\n  setTimeout(() => {\n    console.log('C');\n    E();\n    F();\n    G();\n  },0);\n}\nfunction D() {\n  console.log('D');\n}\nfunction E() {\n  console.log('E');\n}\nfunction F() {\n  console.log('F');\n}\nfunction G() {\n  console.log('G');\n}\nA();\nB();\nC();\nD();\n",[48,226,227,238,251,256,265,279,284,294,306,321,330,338,346,356,361,371,385,390,400,414,419,429,443,448,458,472,477,485,493,501],{"__ignoreMap":46},[51,228,229,232,235],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,230,231],{"class":65},"function",[51,233,234],{"cla